            "title": "港元定存｜富融銀行推「快閃星期一」優惠　新客可搶25厘超高息率",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"富融銀行推「快閃星期一」優惠，新客可搶25厘超高息港元定存。(富融銀行網圖)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"793\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xKky.ckXLuPw3NFnzEvCAA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc5MztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/5b919722638bd58f43aee7afbeee1a63\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">富融銀行推「快閃星期一」優惠，新客可搶25厘超高息港元定存。(富融銀行網圖)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>中秋</span></span></span></span></span>佳節<span><span><span><span><span>將至，騰訊(700)旗下的</span></span></span></span></span>富融銀行宣布推出「快閃星期一」限時優惠活動。自<span><span><span><span><span>下周一(6日)至12月5日期間，新客戶利用邀請碼「FLASH2025」開戶並存入新資金，即可享有25厘的14天港元定期存款，金額上限5萬元，名額共1,500份，成功開立可獲479元利息。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">同步推15厘及2.85厘港元定存</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了新客戶專屬優惠外，富融銀行也為現有客戶提供搶息機會。不論新舊客戶，只需存入1萬元新資金，即可於下周一中午12時起登入銀行應用程式<span><span><span><span><span>，搶高達15厘的7天港元定期存款，名額為888份，名額有限，搶完即止。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d1d25103-cbb0-367d-a73a-db3c40b4c719-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>另外，</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>富融銀行下周一亦會有4個月2.85厘的港元定期存款供選擇，名額為2,000份，每位客戶可搶60份，適用於新客戶及現有客戶。以上兩個活動日期為2025年10月6日中午12時至10月10日中午12時。</span></span></span></span></span></p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\"><span><span><span>資料來源：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:富融銀行公布;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.fusionbank.com/common/detail.html?key=fusionflash&amp;lang=tc\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">富融銀行公布</a></span></span></span></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/港元定存-富融銀行推-快閃星期一-優惠-新客可搶25厘超高息率/605594?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/港元定存-富融銀行推-快閃星期一-優惠-新客可搶25厘超高息率/605594?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/港元定存-富融銀行推-快閃星期一-優惠-新客可搶25厘超高息率/605594?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E5%AE%9A%E5%AD%98-%E5%AF%8C%E8%9E%8D%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A8-%E5%BF%AB%E9%96%83%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F-%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-%E6%96%B0%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%AF%E6%90%B625%E5%8E%98%E8%B6%85%E9%AB%98%E6%81%AF%E7%8E%87-101200835.html",
